4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to develop expertise in protecting digital environments. The program spans 16 weeks, consisting of 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. It covers foundational skills in Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop